message.body: Oh hello again. This whole txting thing hasn't worked that well for me. How about u?
Hey, yeah. I kind of thought it could be better too. I guess they didn't get enough people in the first place. How's your day going?
And my neighbors woke me up at 5 am.
Do u know of any way of insulating my apt? Lol
I seriously woke up seeing red. So angry.
